itemDisplayName: Deploy a 9 Node, cross Azure Zone, unsecure Windows Service Fabric Cluster
description: This template allows you to deploy an unsecure 7Node, cross AZ Service Fabric Cluster running Windows Server 2016 Datacenter with containers on a Standard_D2_V2 Size VMSS, with network security groups enabled.
summary: This template takes a minimum amount of parameters and deploys a 9 Node, cross Azure Zone Windows Service Fabric Cluster
